## 1.  登入並自動抓取 Token - Admin login (store token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{adminUser}}",
  "password": "{{adminPass}}"
}

### 在登入成功後，自動從伺服器回傳的內容中取出 token，並存入全域變數中，這樣後續的請求就不需要手動貼上 Token

> {% client.global.set("token", response.body.token); %}

## 2. 查詢與列表 (GET) - 用來確認目前系統中有哪些輪胎

### 2-1. List tires (admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/tires
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2-2. Search tires (admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/tires?brand={{brand}}&series={{series}}&size={{size}}&active={{active}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

## 3. 新增、更新與狀態切換 (POST, PUT, PATCH)

### 3-1. Create tire (admin) - 建立一條輪胎資料
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/tires
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "brand": "Bridgestone",
  "series": "ALENZA H/L 33",
  "origin": "日本",
  "size": "225/60 R18",
  "price": 3850,
  "isActive": true
}

### 3-2. Update tire (admin) - 修改指定 {{tireId}} 的輪胎資訊（把價格從 3850 改成 3900）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/tires/{{tireId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "brand": "Bridgestone",
  "series": "ALENZA H/L 33",
  "origin": "日本",
  "size": "225/60 R18",
  "price": 3900,
  "isActive": true
}

### 3-3. Toggle tire active (admin) - 測試局部更新，切換輪胎的 isActive 狀態
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/tires/{{tireId}}/active
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "isActive": false
}